Roger Remote
============

Web app to remote control a PC using a mobile device.  Replaces your keyboard and mouse with the mobile device.

Instructions
============

* Install Java from https://java.com/download
* Download and extract ALL files from https://bitbucket.org/richardsmith/roger-remote/downloads/roger.zip
* Double click roger.exe (Windows) or roger.jar (other platforms).
* If prompted, allow access through firewall.
* Click 'start server'.
* Follow on screen instruction.

Support
=======

Server tested on Mac OS X 10.9.  
Client tested on Android 4.4, iOS 7.1

In theory the server should work on any OS that runs Java, and the client should work on any device that supports HTML5. 